SUB_W15_EVAR_COMM_BOSS_030_CUT_030_040.speaker: Corana_Sitrix
SUB_W15_EVAR_COMM_BOSS_030_CUT_030_040.text:
Alessa... Alessa, look!
It's the Vermillion Bird!

SUB_W15_EVAR_COMM_BOSS_030_CUT_030_043.speaker: Alessa_Sitrix
SUB_W15_EVAR_COMM_BOSS_030_CUT_030_043.text:
Corana... I was able to come back...
to this side...?

SUB_W15_EVAR_COMM_BOSS_030_CUT_030_050.speaker: Alessa_Sitrix
SUB_W15_EVAR_COMM_BOSS_030_CUT_030_050.text:
The Vermillion Bird is soaring through
the sky...just like it did then...

SUB_W15_EVAR_COMM_BOSS_030_CUT_030_060.speaker: Corana_Sitrix
SUB_W15_EVAR_COMM_BOSS_030_CUT_030_060.text:
I think the Vermillion Bird has given you
life—which means we weren't wrong.
It found us worthy.

SUB_W15_EVAR_COMM_BOSS_030_CUT_030_070.speaker: Alessa_Sitrix
SUB_W15_EVAR_COMM_BOSS_030_CUT_030_070.text:
Does this mean it has...forgiven me?
Oh, thank you, Corana—all of this is
happening because of you.
